verbose_text: In addition, postnatal overnutrition in IUGR rats can upregulate DNA methylation levels at specific sites of peroxisome proliferator activated receptor gamma coactivator-1alpha (PGC1alpha), promoting the development of insulin resistance, in which PI3K / Akt activity is reduced.
